{
  "id": "adv_main_02_07_03",
  "title": "東京編2章8話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロに全面的に協力するの、賛成です！\n安月給だけど、他に選択の余地もないですしね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Full-scale cooperation with Hoshimi Productions? I’m in!\nThe pay is cheap‚ but it’s not like we have other options.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.633333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "……って、愛ちゃんが言ってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That’s what Ai-chan said.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.833333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "そんなこと言ってないから！\n私は純粋に、一蓮托生で頑張ろうって気持ちです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never said that!\nI just want to work together in solidarity with everyone!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.233333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫よ、ちゃんと分かっているから\nこころ、後で腹筋五十回ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t worry. We understand what you meant.\nKokoro‚ give me 50 sit-ups later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "とにかく、二人も賛成してくれて嬉しいわ\nありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ I’m glad you both are on board.\nThank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.033333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "いえ……実際、バンプロはあんな状態ですから\n姫野さんのことも、よく分からなくなっちゃいましたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh… Given the state that Van Productions is in right now\nand the odd way Himeno-san has been acting and all…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "霧子は昔から、ああいう悪巧みが得意な人だったよ\n正直、ずっと気が合わなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kiriko always had a talent for that kind of sleazy intrigue.\nTo be honest‚ I never liked her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですね……\n全然気付かなかったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ wow…\nI totally didn’t notice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "愛ちゃんはバカ正直で素直ないい子だからね～\n気付けないのも仕方ないよ、大丈夫大丈夫",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s because you’re stupid-honest and nice to a fault‚ Ai-chan.\nI don’t blame you for not noticing. It’s cool‚ it’s cool.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "バカは余計！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Stupid” isn’t a compliment!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.43333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "自分の目的のためには手段を選ばない\n……そういうところのある人よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’ll do whatever it takes to achieve her goals.\nHimeno-san has that dark side to her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "だからこそ、あの人のやり方は近い将来\n必ずアイドル業界を腐敗させる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s exactly why her way of doing things\nwill corrupt the idol industry in the near future.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "何をするつもりかは全然分からないけど\n好き勝手させる訳にはいかないね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have no idea what she’s trying to do‚\nbut we definitely can’t let her get away with it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_main-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 78.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんです！\nお父さんを喜ばせるために、この業界に入ったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course!\nI joined showbiz to make my father happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "胸を張れない業界でトップアイドルになっても\n意味なんかこれっぽっちもありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I became an idol in an industry I couldn’t take pride in‚\nthere wouldn’t be a speck of meaning to it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "愛……ふふっ。私も気持ちは同じ\n精一杯、アイドル業界を盛り上げていきましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ Ai. Hehe. I feel the same way.\nLet’s put our hearts into hyping up the idol industry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "この新しい居場所――\n星見プロで、みんなと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At this new place.\nAt Hoshimi Productions‚ all together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "もっちろんです～\n愛ちゃんのこと、ビシバシ鍛えてあげて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course!\nDon’t hold back with Ai-chan! Give her your harshest discipline!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあこころには、その三倍頑張ってもらおうかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ Kokoro‚ I guess that means we’ll give you three times that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "えっと～……それなら愛ちゃんは\nちょーっと鍛えてあげるぐらいでいいと思いまーす",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uhhh… In that case‚ I think Ai-chan\nonly needs a teeeeeny-tiny bit of discipline.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "まったく……\nいつどこにいたって、こころはこころのままだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Jeez…\nNo matter where she goes‚ our Koroko never changes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "あの……莉央ちゃん、葵ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… Rio-chan‚ Aoi-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_liz-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 129.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、ごめんなさい\nすっかり私達だけで話し込んじゃったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ sorry.\nWe slipped off into our own conversation there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、グループにとって大事なお話でしょうし\n……終わりましたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s okay. You’ve got important matters to discuss as a group.\n…Did you finish?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "うん、話はついたよ\n待たせてごめんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ we tied things up.\nSorry we made you wait.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "さっそく、レッスンを再開しましょうか\n今日は私達が面倒見てあげるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shall we jump right back into our lessons?\nWe’ll look after everyone today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "アメリカ仕込みの\nブートキャンプもびっくりなレッスンプログラムだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a lesson plan\nthat even shocked the bootcamp instructors in the U.S.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_03-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "ついてこれるかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can you keep up?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はいっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2366.6666666666742,
          "startTime": 161.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 161.16666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_unrest-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 161.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
